column2: "My name is Huey! I'm the sixth of the Council of Six!"
"Hm? I somehow get the sense that I've met you before! Did I?"
"Well details don't really matter! More importantly, is there anything I can help you with?"
"Even though I'm in the Council of Six, all I ever do is help other people. I don't have anything else to do!"
"Everyone else in the Council of Six is pretty much the opposite, they have way too much on their hands to handle!"
"The Council of Six is selected solely on power. To act as a role model for the rest of the organization!"
"Hm, I sense some photons in distress! I must go assist, may we meet again!"
